<plot>A romantic comedy about an ugly yet friendly zombie named Ghoulee, who is suffering from a sad lack of female companionship. After living for centuries without affection from anyone, Ghoulee musters up the nerve to go Bar hopping in a desperate attempt to procure a lady who might be willing to give up a little love and affection in celebration of Valentine s Day. Ghoulee is told by a bar patron that the only way to get affection on Valentine s Day is to give a woman roses, chocolates and a valentine bear. Armed with that advice, Ghoulee steals a valentine bear, some candy and roses and begins his mentally unclear, odyssey, desperately searching for a little love and affection from an available lady among a sea of unmerciful witches, gypsies and geisha girls.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?635368</url></doc>
